4.3.40.name: wordpress/blogrollsync
4.3.40.description:
This plugin is only supported on PHP 5.2 or greater.

LinkSync allows you to easily synchronise the links list on multiple blogs with one central site. Making it easier to maintain multiple blogs.

If you are having trouble and cannot find the answers in the FAQ you can post your support questions to the WordPress Support Forum

If you find LinkSync useful please rate it at wordpress.org and please consider making a donation to help us set aside more hours to maintain LinkSync

LinkSync is written by dcoda

You can check out our other plugins here

If you require a custom plugin you can contact us
